#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int n,i; 
vector<string> data;
int main()
{
	cin>>n;
string t;
	for(i=0;i<n;i++)
	{
		cin>>t;
		data.push_back(t);
	}
	sort(data.begin(),data.end());
 
	for(i=0;i<n-1;i++)
	{
		int j=i+1;
		int pos = data[j].find(data[i]);
 
		if(pos == 0)
		{
			cout<<"vulnerable"<<endl;
			return 0;
		}
 
	}
 
	cout<<"non vulnerable"<<endl;
 
}
